♪Please don't wake her♪

11
00:01:02,310 --> 00:01:06,240
♪From her dreamland♪

12
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,340
♪Hopes held close♪

13
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:10,060
♪Safe and sound♪

14
